# Mohammed Hamdan AlShehhi - Ladies Tailoring & Embroidery

**Traditional Women's Wear Jalabiya | Dubai**

---

## Project Overview

This repository contains the complete professional all-in-one website for **Mohammed Hamdan AlShehhi**, including:  

- Unlimited products display with automatic image adjustments and 3D viewing  
- AI chat integration  
- Customer management and newsletter subscription  
- Website completion tracker and QA checker  
- Firebase analytics  
- Fully automated scripts for image editing, Git commits, and multi-file management  

---

## Features

### 1. Web Pages
- `index.html` – Homepage with social media links and product overview  
- `products.html` – Add/Remove products with 3D/slider view  
- `tracker.html` – Website task completion tracker  
- `ultimate-website-final-launch.html` – All-in-one final launch page  

### 2. JS & Python Automation Scripts
- `auto-editor.js` / `auto-editor-v2.js` – Automatic image adjustments  
- `auto-commit-all-v2.py` – Git commit automation  
- `multi-file-auto-commit.py` / `multi-file-commit.py` – Multi-file Git operations  
- `git_auto_commit_scalable.py` – Scalable Git automation  
- `git_commit_gui_pro.py` – GUI tool for Git commit  
- `newfile_products_update.py` – Batch product updates  

### 3. Styles & Config
- `style.css` – Professional website styling  
- `CNAME` – Custom domain configuration  
- `index.html` – Root homepage  

---

